quran[24{c,v,t}:
37,103,jab dono ne hukum maan liya aur baap ne betay ko maathey ke bil luta diya
37,104,to hum ne un ko puraka ke ae ibrahim
37,105,tum ne khawab ko sacha kar dekhaya. hum naiko karon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
37,106,bilashuba yeh Sarih azmaish thi
37,107,aur hum ne aik barri qurbani ko un ka Fidya diya
37,108,aur peechay anay walon mein ibrahim ka ( zikar kher baqi ) chore diya
37,109,ke ibrahim par salam ho
37,110,naiko karon ko hum aisa hi badla diya karte hain
37,111,woh hamaray momin bundon mein se they
37,112,aur hum ne un ko Ishaq ki basharat bhi di ( ke woh ) nabi ( aur ) naiko karon mein se ( hon ge )
37,113,aur hum ne un par aur Ishaq par barkaten nazil ki theen. aur un dono aulaad ki mein se nekokaar bhi hain aur apne aap par Sarih zulm karne walay ( yani gunehgaar ) bhi hain
37,114,aur hum ne moose aur Haroon par bhi ahsaan kiye
37,115,aur un ko aur un ki qoum ko museebat Azima se nijaat bakhsh
37,116,aur un ki madad ki to woh ghalib hogaye
37,117,aur un dono ko kitaab wazeh (ul matalib ) inayat ki
37,118,aur un ko seedha rasta dekhaya
37,119,aur peechay anay walon mein un ka zikar ( kher baqi ) chore diya
37,120,ke moose aur Haroon par salam
37,121,be shak hum naiko karon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
37,122,woh dono hamaray momin bundon mein se they
37,123,aur Ilyas bhi payghambaroon mein se they
37,124,jab unhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke tum drtay kyun nahi ?
37,125,kiya tum b - al ko pkarte ( aur usay pujte ) ho aur sab se behtar peda karne walay ko chore dete ho
37,126,( yani ) khuda ko jo tumhara aur tumahray aglay baap dada ka perwar-digaar hai
